<data>&lt;div class=b&gt;&lt;a href="/"&gt;Home&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/15A4"&gt;15A4 Catukkanipātapāḷi&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/15A4/2"&gt;2 Dutiyapaṇṇāsaka&lt;/a&gt; » &lt;a href="/tipitaka/15A4/2/2.1"&gt;2.1 Puññābhisandavagga&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="i"&gt;2.1.9 Bhojanasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Dutiyapaṇṇāsaka&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Puññābhisandavagga&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class=h&gt;Bhojanasutta&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_15A4_427"&gt; &lt;div class="divNumber"&gt;59.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;427&lt;/span&gt;“Bhojanaṃ, bhikkhave, dadamāno dāyako paṭiggāhakānaṃ cattāri ṭhānāni deti. Katamāni cattāri? Āyuṃ deti, vaṇṇaṃ deti, sukhaṃ deti, balaṃ deti. Āyuṃ kho pana datvā āyussa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. Vaṇṇaṃ datvā…  sukhaṃ datvā…  balaṃ datvā balassa bhāgī hoti dibbassa vā mānusassa vā. Bhojanaṃ, bhikkhave, dadamāno dāyako paṭiggāhakānaṃ imāni cattāri ṭhānāni detīti. &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_15A4_428"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;428&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Yo saññatānaṃ paradattabhojinaṃ,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Kālena sakkacca dadāti bhojanaṃ;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Cattāri ṭhānāni anuppavecchati,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Āyuñca vaṇṇañca sukhaṃ balañca.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="q" id="p_15A4_429"&gt; &lt;div class="p"&gt; &lt;table class="singleColumn"&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="pN"&gt;429&lt;/div&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;So āyudāyī vaṇṇadāyī,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;sukhaṃ balaṃ dado naro;&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;Dīghāyu yasavā hoti,&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;tr&gt; &lt;td&gt; &lt;div class="G"&gt;yattha yatthūpapajjatī”ti.&lt;/div&gt; &lt;/td&gt; &lt;/tr&gt; &lt;/table&gt; &lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="CENTER" id="p_15A4_430"&gt;&lt;span class="pN"&gt;430&lt;/span&gt;Navamaṃ.&lt;/div&gt;&lt;div class="tn"&gt;&lt;div class=plcb&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="prevP()" id="prevL" name="275580" title="Go to previous page"&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt; 2.1.8 Sudattasutta&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="upP()" id="upL" name="273117" title="Go to parent page"&gt;up&lt;/a&gt;&lt;a href="javascript:void(0)" onclick="nextP()" id="nextL" name="275582" title="Go to next page"&gt;2.1.10 Gihisāmīcisutta &amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</data>
